Description: A lightweight dock for Linux
 Docking is a Python GTK3 dock inspired by Plank and Cairo-Dock.
 Features parabolic zoom, window previews, autohide, drag-and-drop,
 and an extensible applet system with 9 built-in applets (clock,
 trash, weather, CPU monitor, battery, clipboard, applications,
 network, show desktop).
 .
 Requires X11.
